#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/internals/020-package-release.md
msgid "No critical issues."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/internals/020-package-release.md
msgid "Public API changes aren't likely. Some time passed w/o issues reported that may require API changes."
